name: 9TU20 - Inner Planet Emanator
description:
Emanators is an ancient species collection, composed of 4 sealed scrolls, 
that portraits visions of different types of non-human existances that once existed in unkown cosmic regions and eons. 

Series developed exclusivelly for Here and Now edition 4 metaverse exhibition.

2500 x 4000 - 300 dpi
